# ── Rust build output ───────────────────────────────────────────────
/target/
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb
sample
# Keep Cargo.lock tracked (Orchester ships binaries).
.cargo
# ── Forschung: cloned reference repos ───────────────────────────────
# 50+ upstream repos live here purely as read-only reference. Never commit
# them (each carries its own .git). Keep only our own analysis + notes.
/forschung/*
!/forschung/ANALYSIS.md
!/forschung/README.md
# Legacy name before the German rename (belt & braces):
/agent-research/
/forschung/.analysis_parts/

# ── Local runtime / tooling state ───────────────────────────────────
.remember/logs/
.remember/tmp/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
tmp/

